exd5 18. Rfe1 Kd8
{ After  18...dxe4  19.Qxe4+  Be7   @@StartBracket@@and  19...Qe7  20.Qc4  followed by  Bc5+  is also fatal for him@@EndBracket@@  20.Bc5  Black is definitely missing his right to castling.   As for  18...Be7  , White breaks through by  19.Nd6+  Kf8   @@StartBracket@@or  19...Qxd6  20.Bc5  @@EndBracket@@  20.Nf5  Bf6  21.Bc5+  Kg8  22.Re7  and  22...--  23.Rae1  next. }
