15. f3 { Clearing the e-file and the long diagonal towards Black's camp. }
15... e3
{ Now in the event of  15...cxd4  16.fxe4  Qxe5  , White has  17.Rxf5  Qe6  18.Qxd4  with the double threat of  Qxg7+  and  Re5  . }
16. Rfe1 Kf6 { Or  16...cxd4  17.Rxd4  Qxe5  18.f4  , winning - Golubev. } 17.
dxc5 Qxe5 18. Rd6+ Ke7 19. Qh4+ Kf7 20. Qc4+
{ In view of  20.Qc4+  Ke7  21.f4  Qxc5  22.Qe6+  Kf8  23.Rd8  , Black resigned. }
