f6 15. Bb5 Qb6 { The pressure at  d7  is unbearable; e.g.  15...Qc7  16.Bf4 }
16. Kc1 fxg5 17. Bxd7+ Kf8 18. Rxe7 Kxe7 19. Qe4+ Kd8
