14. c4
{ Clearing the centre and preparing actions on the a4-e8 diagonal before Black manages to castle. }
14... cxd4
{ After  14...dxc4  15.d5   Or  14...Nxd4  15.Nxd4  cxd4  16.cxd5  exd5  17.Nf4  Black is also in trouble. }
