12... e5
{ 12...Bg7  13.e5  Nh5   @@StartBracket@@or  13...dxe5  14.Nxe5  Qc8  15.Ne4  with irresistible pressure.@@EndBracket@@  14.exd6  exd6  15.Rfe1+  Kf8  16.Bxd7  Qxd7  17.Qb5  A strong blow that finishes off Black's resistance. In view of his desperate position after  17...Qxb5  18.Bxd6+  Kg8  19.axb5  Black resigned. }
13. dxe6 Nxe6 { Was a lesser evil, justifying the knight on d8. After } 14. e5
Nxf4 15. exf6 Ne6 16. Rfe1 O-O-O
