[White "2.1 Early Pawn-Grabbing"]
[Black "Early pawn-grabbing"]
[Result "*"]

{ @@HeaderStart@@Early pawn-grabbing@@HeaderEnd@@ } 1. --
{ We already saw one related case in Dvoretsky-Schmidt. Here are a few more games where one side suffers badly from early pawn-grabbing. }
