[Black "Exercise #1: A.Vaisser-M.Illescas"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1b1k2r/ppq2ppp/2nb1n2/1BppN3/Q2P4/2N1P3/PP3PPP/R1B1K2R b KQkq - 0 9"]
[SetUp "1"]

O-O
{ A key decision. Black sacrifices a pawn in order to speed up development. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
