6. Nxe5 Bxe5 7. c3
{ The inherent plan of the Rossolimo: create a pawn centre with d2-d4. } 7...
a6 8. Bf1 d6 9. d4 cxd4 10. cxd4 Bg7 11. Nc3 Nf6 12. Bg5 O-O
{ By the admittedly unsound  12...h6  13.Bh4  g5  14.Bg3  O-O  Black could have reached a safer version of the game. }
