{ Returning home doesn't seem right in this fluid position.   Nowadays,  5.Ne4  is a much more popular way of meeting Black's gambit. }
5... Bf5 6. Qb3
{ Hunting pawns at a very early stage of the game.   6.Nf3  was better of course. }
6... Na6 7. Qxb7 Nb4 8. Na3 Rb8 9. Qxa7 Ra8 10. Qb7
