8. Na4
{ Exploiting the fresh weakness on b6.   Instead,  8.Rc1  Nc6  9.Na4  is less accurate due to  9...Bb4+  with ...Ba5 as an extra resource. }
8... Ra7
{ This won't end well; but after  8...Nd7  9.Rc1  Qd8  10.Qxb7  Black's game is also terrible. }
9. Nb6 Qd8 10. Bxb8
{ The immediate  10.Qa4+  failed to  10...Nc6  , so White prepares it. } 10...
Qxb8 11. Qa4+ Ke7 12. Rc1 g5 { Desperation in a lost position. } 13. Ne5 Nh6
14. Nc8+ { In view of  14.Nc8+  Kf6  15.Nd7+  , Black resigned. } *

