[Result "*"]

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 c5 4. Nf3
{ White turns down the invitation to a Benoni with  4.d5  , and heads for the English. }
4... cxd4 5. Nxd4 b6
{ Black takes the first step to a Hedgehog formation with ...Bb7, ...d7-d6, ...Nbd7 etc; but in this case  5...d6  or  5...a6  was more advisable. }
6. --
