16. Bxe6
{ This sacrifice decides the game.   Obviously  16.fxe3  Qe7  would be less powerful. }
16... exd2+ 17. Rxd2 fxe6 18. Qg6+ Ke7 19. Re1 Kd6
{ Heading for c7, but in vain... } 20. d5
{ A timely advance that includes the second rook in the attack. In view of  20.d5  cxd5  21.Rxe6+  Kc7  22.Nxd5+  Kc8  23.Re8  , Black resigned. }
