{ A modern alternative to 6...Nd7, by which Black keeps the option of ...c6-c5 and ...Nc6 on some occasions. }
7. h4 h6 8. h5
{ White proceeds like in the main line with 6...Nd7.   Probably  8.Ne5  is more critical. }
