17... a5
{ With the centre under complete command, Black launches an attack on the fragile enemy queenside. }
18. Bg2
{ This leads to a soon collapse of White's position; but  18.Nb6  Qc3+  19.Bd2  Nxd2  20.Qxd2  Rb8  - Volkov   Or  18.b5  cxb5  19.Qxb5+  Bd7  was also bad for him. }
18... axb4 19. Nb6 Ra3 20. Qc2 Rxe3
{ A final detail, which leaves White without protection on the dark squares. }
21. Nxc8 Rc3 22. Qb1 O-O 23. Nb6 Nxf2 24. Kxf2 Bh4+
{ In view of  24...Bh4+  25.Kf1  Qf4+  26.Bf3  Rxf3+  or  26...Qg3  , White resigned. }
