10... Qd7 11. Nxe4 Bxe4
{ Or  11...dxe4  12.Ng5  , winning a pawn, since  12...Qd5  runs into  13.c4  .   After  11...Bxe4  Black was perhaps hoping for  12.Ng5   @@StartBracket@@or  12.Nd4  c5  @@EndBracket@@  Bf5  , followed by ...e7-e6, but Keres has a much stronger move prepared. }
